name: Geospatial
description: A system for collecting, managing and analyzing data related to location

name: GIS-Database
description: A database for storing location-based data

name: Data-Layers
description: An array of data layers stored in the GIS database

name: GIS-Operations
description: Activities related to the management of GIS data

name: Data-Management
description: Processes related to the creation, collection, storage, and dissemination of spatial data

name: Open-Data
description: Publicly available data that can be accessed and used by anyone

name: Location
description: An object that has a identifiable position

name: Transportation-Network
description: A collection of transportation infrastructure such as roads and trails

name: Roads
description: A network of paved or unpaved routes for vehicular transport

name: Trails
description: A network of paths for cycling, hiking, or other non-motorized travel
